{
  "video_id": "vdo0h3DQQmw",
  "title": "How to Change Bad Habits and Become a Better You",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 260.0,
      "end_time": 2600.0,
      "text": "A habit is a fixed way of thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2600.0,
      "end_time": 4700.0,
      "text": "that leads to automatic behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4700.0,
      "end_time": 8980.0,
      "text": "The benefit is we don’t have to rethink again and again what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8980.0,
      "end_time": 11960.0,
      "text": "It just happens and can have good side effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12180.0,
      "end_time": 14360.0,
      "text": "But a bad habit can also hurt us"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14360.0,
      "end_time": 16420.0,
      "text": "or hold us back from progressing."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16420.0,
      "end_time": 19980.0,
      "text": "Although, like anything, we can learn and unlearn them."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20180.0,
      "end_time": 24020.0,
      "text": "But first, let's try to understand where they come from."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 25300.0,
      "end_time": 27620.0,
      "text": "Habits are made by experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 27620.0,
      "end_time": 30780.0,
      "text": "creating fixed ways of thinking inside our brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30860.0,
      "end_time": 31820.0,
      "text": "To explain this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31820.0,
      "end_time": 34240.0,
      "text": "let's compare what happens inside your brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34240.0,
      "end_time": 36180.0,
      "text": "to what happens on a farm."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36500.0,
      "end_time": 38380.0,
      "text": "There is a farmer named Joe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 38380.0,
      "end_time": 39820.0,
      "text": "his vegetable garden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 39820.0,
      "end_time": 42400.0,
      "text": "the chicken shed and a mailbox."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 42600.0,
      "end_time": 46440.0,
      "text": "Every morning farmer Joe first walks to the vegetables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 46440.0,
      "end_time": 48220.0,
      "text": "then checks on his chickens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 48220.0,
      "end_time": 51740.0,
      "text": "then collects his mail  and then walks back to the house."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 51960.0,
      "end_time": 54100.0,
      "text": "After a few days of this routine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54100.0,
      "end_time": 56980.0,
      "text": "his trace becomes more visible on his farm."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57200.0,
      "end_time": 60800.0,
      "text": "After a few months, the trace becomes fixed pathways."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60800.0,
      "end_time": 64420.0,
      "text": "Not only on his farm, but also inside his brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66360.0,
      "end_time": 69120.0,
      "text": "One night Joe has a magical dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69120.0,
      "end_time": 72460.0,
      "text": "where he discovers his love with all living creatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72460.0,
      "end_time": 75360.0,
      "text": "The next day he sets all of his chickens free."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75360.0,
      "end_time": 76720.0,
      "text": "The funny thing is though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76720.0,
      "end_time": 78840.0,
      "text": "instead of adjusting his behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78840.0,
      "end_time": 82740.0,
      "text": "he still walks blindly from the vegetable garden to the chicken shed."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82960.0,
      "end_time": 86000.0,
      "text": "The trace on the ground, and inside Joe’s brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86000.0,
      "end_time": 88020.0,
      "text": "are now just too deep."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88360.0,
      "end_time": 92180.0,
      "text": "To leave the path of habit, we have to go down a new road."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92380.0,
      "end_time": 96800.0,
      "text": "This takes time  multiple repetitions of our new desired behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96800.0,
      "end_time": 99540.0,
      "text": "and willpower to keep going."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100960.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "A habit is often a response to a certain trigger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104380.0,
      "end_time": 108460.0,
      "text": "which follows a routine and usually ends with a reward."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108620.0,
      "end_time": 110900.0,
      "text": "This is also called a habit loop."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111220.0,
      "end_time": 113400.0,
      "text": "Joe’s trigger is the vegetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113400.0,
      "end_time": 115780.0,
      "text": "As soon as he waters the last tomato,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115780.0,
      "end_time": 119660.0,
      "text": "he starts his next routine to automatically walk to the chickens."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119840.0,
      "end_time": 122080.0,
      "text": "His reward is to find eggs."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122200.0,
      "end_time": 124580.0,
      "text": "And because rewards release dopamine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124580.0,
      "end_time": 128940.0,
      "text": "a neurotransmitter that makes our brain first happy and then hooked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128940.0,
      "end_time": 131600.0,
      "text": "we get stuck and can’t let go anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133340.0,
      "end_time": 135480.0,
      "text": "Joe's sister lives in the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135660.0,
      "end_time": 137300.0,
      "text": "She has a funny habit."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137300.0,
      "end_time": 139280.0,
      "text": "Whenever she hears her phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139280.0,
      "end_time": 141680.0,
      "text": "she automatically looks at the screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 141680.0,
      "end_time": 145180.0,
      "text": "Most of the time it's just a random irrelevant message."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145180.0,
      "end_time": 147960.0,
      "text": "This happens even if something far more important"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 147960.0,
      "end_time": 150020.0,
      "text": "was happening right in that moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150340.0,
      "end_time": 154760.0,
      "text": "The sound from the phone  triggers a routine in the hope for a sweet reward"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154760.0,
      "end_time": 157300.0,
      "text": "and some of that addictive dopamine."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158640.0,
      "end_time": 164400.0,
      "text": "To change a habit, journalist Charles Duhigg recommends redesigning the habit loop."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164560.0,
      "end_time": 166900.0,
      "text": "Say you like going to the movie theater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166900.0,
      "end_time": 171000.0,
      "text": "but whenever you do, you eat too much of that sweet popcorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 171000.0,
      "end_time": 173440.0,
      "text": "In this case your trigger is the popcorn"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173440.0,
      "end_time": 176460.0,
      "text": "stand that you pass by whenever you go to the movies."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176640.0,
      "end_time": 179440.0,
      "text": "Your routine is buying that popcorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179580.0,
      "end_time": 182540.0,
      "text": "And your reward is snacking during the film."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182780.0,
      "end_time": 184040.0,
      "text": "To change your habit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184040.0,
      "end_time": 186600.0,
      "text": "you could keep the trigger  and keep the reward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186600.0,
      "end_time": 188320.0,
      "text": "but replace the routine."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188560.0,
      "end_time": 191240.0,
      "text": "Instead of sweet, get salty popcorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191420.0,
      "end_time": 193860.0,
      "text": "Later maybe even fruits."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 195140.0,
      "end_time": 197200.0,
      "text": "If a problem gets very serious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 197200.0,
      "end_time": 198620.0,
      "text": "remove the trigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198780.0,
      "end_time": 200640.0,
      "text": "Stop buying movie tickets."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 200900.0,
      "end_time": 202820.0,
      "text": "If we can’t leave our phone alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 202820.0,
      "end_time": 205320.0,
      "text": "we can turn off all the notifications."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205500.0,
      "end_time": 208320.0,
      "text": "And if we have friends that get us into situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 208320.0,
      "end_time": 210040.0,
      "text": "that can trigger a bad habit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 210040.0,
      "end_time": 212820.0,
      "text": "we can make new friends that don’t."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 214120.0,
      "end_time": 215820.0,
      "text": "Some habits are tricky."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 215980.0,
      "end_time": 217920.0,
      "text": "Procrastination for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 217920.0,
      "end_time": 221400.0,
      "text": "There is no clear trigger, routine or reward."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 221400.0,
      "end_time": 222940.0,
      "text": "It just happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 222940.0,
      "end_time": 225740.0,
      "text": "Habits like that can be changed in tiny steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 225740.0,
      "end_time": 227620.0,
      "text": "that leads to small rewards."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 227760.0,
      "end_time": 229640.0,
      "text": "Next time you procrastinate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 229640.0,
      "end_time": 232860.0,
      "text": "try to make some short breaks in which you focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 232860.0,
      "end_time": 235660.0,
      "text": "Your trigger can be the full hour on your clock."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 235880.0,
      "end_time": 238100.0,
      "text": "Once you hear it, focus on your work"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 238100.0,
      "end_time": 240420.0,
      "text": "even if it is just for 5 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 240420.0,
      "end_time": 243640.0,
      "text": "After, reward yourself with a piece of chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 243800.0,
      "end_time": 245740.0,
      "text": "The very first day you do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 245740.0,
      "end_time": 248700.0,
      "text": "you will already create some new traces in your brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248700.0,
      "end_time": 250540.0,
      "text": "and the next day some more."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250700.0,
      "end_time": 254720.0,
      "text": "After a few weeks, it will be easy to walk down that road."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 256060.0,
      "end_time": 260520.0,
      "text": "Many small steps added together, make a big difference over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 260519.99999999997,
      "end_time": 264220.0,
      "text": "After all, we still have our entire life in front of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264220.0,
      "end_time": 268520.0,
      "text": "And to becomes successful, good habits are probably our best bet."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 268780.0,
      "end_time": 271420.0,
      "text": "As the famous poet John Dryden wrote:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 271420.0,
      "end_time": 275320.0,
      "text": "“We first make our habits,  and then our habits make us.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275720.0,
      "end_time": 279240.0,
      "text": "Tell us. Have you ever learn or unlearned a habit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279240.0,
      "end_time": 282880.0,
      "text": "Please share your experience in the comments below!"
    }
  ]
}